	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />In Mother there are 2 impressive graphical effects before the final boss fight that I thought were impossible on the NES!<br /><br />1) Apparently 2 BG layers<br />2) SNES-like &quot;mosaic&quot; effect<br /><br />Any info on this?<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wz6Ueh39A1g">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wz6Ueh39A1g</a><!-- m -->

		

		</td>
	</tr>
