	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Mother uses MMC3, so probably using the scanline counter to do a timed screen split at the 'ground' area. Mosaic effect is probably CHR bank switching.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


