	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you want to be able to do mosaic everywhere (as on certain SNES games) without the bus masking, then it'd take a quadrupling of CHR ROM size or specialized hardware to queue up CHR RAM rewrites and execute them during dead times in the scanline.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
